      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p><i>14th-level Circle of Wildfire feature</i></p><p>The bond with your wildfire spirit can save you from death. If the spirit is within 120 feet of you when you are reduced to 0 hit points and thereby fall &amp;Reference[condition=unconscious], you can cause the spirit to drop to 0 hit points. You then regain half your hit points and immediately rise to your feet.</p><p>Once you use this feature, you can't use it again until you finish a long rest.</p></div>",
